            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"glm-hmm-model-recovery\">GLM-HMM Model Recovery</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Goal</strong>: verify that EM can recover known ground-truth parameters.</span>\n<ol>\n<li>Choose a subject &amp; K \u2192 load its real trial covariates X</li>\n<li>Define true emission weights <strong>W</strong> and transition matrix <strong>A</strong></li>\n<li>Simulate synthetic choices on top of the real trial structure</li>\n<li>Fit with EM</li>\n<li>Compare fitted \u2194 true parameters</li>\n</ol></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
